README.portier_spooling
----------------------------

if enabled the communication between core and portier (e.g. upstreaming of notifictaions or orch communication)
is spooled to a given directory.

you can call sbin/bartlby_portier_spool_bulk.php via a cronjob to work threw the queue - and kick out doublettes.

tools:
	sbin/bartlby_portier_spool_bulk.php

config vars:
	* portier_spool_dir
	* portier_spool_commands